  <body>
    <div class="intro">
      <h1>Kitten OR Puppy?</h1>
      <h2>answering the question that matters most</h2>
      <p>
        Cats and dogs are the most popular pets in the world. <br/>
        The unending rivalry between them won't end today,
        but thanks to your input we're going to at least find out which pet
        seems to be more popular.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>How are we gonna do it?</strong><br/>
        We took pictures of <a href="https://imgur.com/r/kittens">kittens</a> and <a href="https://imgur.com/r/puppies">puppies</a> and you shall vote by clicking
        on image of your liking.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>
          <%= @vote_count %> clicks
          and right now it's
          <% if @kitten_percent > 50 %>
            <%= @kitten_percent %>/<%= 100 - @kitten_percent %> for kittens!
          <% elsif @kitten_percent < 50 %>
            <%= 100 - @kitten_percent %>/<%= @kitten_percent %> for puppies!
          <% else %>
            50/50
          <% end %>
        </strong>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="kitten">
      <a href="/vote/<%= @kitten_id%>">
        <img src=<%= @kitten_url %> alt="Kitten" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="puppy">
      <a href="/vote/<%= @puppy_id%>">
        <img src=<%= @puppy_url %> alt="Puppy" />
      </a>
